title: Dreamland - 05-15-10 - Love, Esp, The Cia And The Meaning Of Lif
description: Anne Strieber has a phenomenal discussion with one of the originators of remote viewing, Russell Targ. You will meet this amazing and important human being in a whole new way, in intimate conversation with somebody who knows just what questions to ask. A friend of people like Alan Alda, Ayn Rand, Alan Greenspan and the brother-in-law of chess champion Bobby Fisher, Targ has developed what he calls 'Five Keys to Liberation' that enable us to see beyond the limits of ordinary perception into a new world of meaning and joy.
